title: Tech tennis back returns to action with a Sunday doubleheader at No. 19 Mississippi State - Tennessee Tech
content: Tech tennis back returns to action with a Sunday doubleheader at No. 19 Mississippi State  Tennessee Tech
description: Following a near month-long layoff after its opening day doubleheader, the Tennessee Tech tennis team is finally back in action for another twin bill, as the Golden Eagles head to No. 19 Mississippi State for a Sunday double dip with the Bulldogs.
